    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 16.924002,
      "replayEndSec": 20.590881,
      "narrationText": "Paso tres: sube la configuración al servidor. Con un token real, esto crea tus registros DNS en Cloudflare automáticamente y prepara la configuración del proxy.",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-03.0d36f96f.mp3",
      "textHash": "0d36f96fe8d08dca1eb096a465626836c3e103327e8b3f36be9483bf85386b30",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.546122,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-03-after.9c53fb91.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.440816,
      "afterTextHash": "9c53fb91745ec6c42f3b4aad979a636a5d16e0020224cf31f98a7c0474e2cc54"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 20.590881,
      "replayEndSec": 28.48077,
      "narrationText": "Paso cuatro: crea un repo pequeño llamado infra. ¿Por qué su propio repo? El proxy enruta el tráfico de cada app en este servidor. La infraestructura merece su propia caja aislada, lejos del código de tu aplicación.",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-04.77c5c09f.mp3",
      "textHash": "77c5c09fdb2998a18a9c1b65e0fd48dd60f541270fac9f8ba91e245f2c91e453",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.386122,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-04-after.2d5ad60d.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 6.765714,
      "afterTextHash": "2d5ad60dfff9dbf5699aa1cc7dafaa1f39c18d1e00fa5489f9a56d7ef680141f"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 28.48077,
      "replayEndSec": 35.97937,
      "narrationText": "Aplicamos la plantilla de proxy integrada. Incluye Traefik más la configuración para Let's Encrypt y los desafíos DNS guion 01 de Cloudflare, lista para usar.",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-05.5cacdbb2.mp3",
      "textHash": "5cacdbb23c17004f50e4ed56a83d2c492802fead0f247495994689c47bb4b3d6",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.930612,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-05-after.12961110.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.507755,
      "afterTextHash": "12961110d369bec396a1f42655ee25b8a1b3b3c1d0c76dd7f36fb1e0f75cc764"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 35.97937,
      "replayEndSec": 42.626799,
      "narrationText": "Y levantamos el proxy. Traefik descubre tus contenedores cada cinco segundos. Los certificados TLS vienen de Let's Encrypt automáticamente. Tu app es ahora accesible en internet por HTTPS.",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-06.ee60edfc.mp3",
      "textHash": "ee60edfcf272304b55c08654d966a6a7756051c95d606bd205f4ff5f9c06658c",
      "audioDurationSec": 16.587755,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-06-after.90a9b3a8.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.597551,
